## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms. The findings are based on available literature and may not capture the latest trends or emerging platforms. Additionally, the influence of social media can vary significantly across different regions and industries, which may not be fully represented in this report.